{"tid":335162,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 FIFA17 Pro Club招防中","createTime":"2017-07-25T11:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T06:35:08.000Z","uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2290e41c1c150d457f6d19521f7e5b83d2ecbef","tid":335162,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"我地隊波基本上穩守D1，暫時攞過1次D1冠<br />\n主打快速短傳同走位波<br />\n<br />\n依家想招一個主力防守嘅防中，增強中場嘅防守力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時就同2個中堅配合，當3個中堅咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地全部人都主張輕鬆足球，唔會串嘴，唔會失波就爆哂粗怪責隊友，大家吹住水開心踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n逢星期1~5 9點9倒開波<br />\n星期6，日踢到嘅都會踢<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打可以留低tg，方便聯絡同試腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecd81bb5c5e3d7f8b7037ed38f546472d559561","tid":335162,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"仲有想招多1個右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴打可以留低tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139813cca18475f3af2efef8f435ae6738e4756","tid":335162,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15bbe46e36fac217fc06dba2d28c79975beb88b","tid":335162,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c5e996078784bdde5aa5a15b7f0f764c3c5201","tid":335162,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905492f2d577ad877e37254a463a0e3916d6d4fe","tid":335162,"uid":130491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl